{"tid":2259169,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Now新聞將港大副校長片段下架　NowTV稱審慎原則作改動","createTime":"2020-10-26T15:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T15:11:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"605520083d67a9166e5e59d68ddfaf0a82eab2dd","tid":2259169,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T15:02:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556742-20201026.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556742-20201026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETZS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=2ad3b267\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556742-20201026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c48d0bbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556742-20201026.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台早前把立法會教育界議員葉建源質詢香港大學副校長受推薦人選，是否有黨員背景的片段下架。<br />\n<br />\nNow TV回應表示，新聞台當日播出相關新聞後，得悉部份內容需待進一步核實，所以基於審慎原則作出若干編輯改動，又提到港大校方亦在當天的回應聲明中指出有媒體報道錯誤。Now TV表示，新聞台昨日繼續更新及報道相關新聞，當中包括葉建源的電話訪問。<br />\n<br />\nNow TV表示，新聞台將繼續聆聽各方意見、公平公正地為市民提供中肯及如實的新聞。"},{"pid":"69bb031cf2e04e667c9e143e6fe9f459457c1c71","tid":2259169,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"THIS?<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/ajt5k2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fajt5k2&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETZS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=00e26a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/ajt5k2</a>"},{"pid":"f10fda0de89b96926a8e179b9871d33badfc19c7","tid":2259169,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"69bb031cf2e04e667c9e143e6fe9f459457c1c71","tid":2259169,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"THIS?<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/ajt5k2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A